tip.text: Will definitely come again. Love this place.
This ice cream with choc popcorn for $6.90. Won't go there and buy again, too pricey for this.
Decks and boots are a great shop to buy hiking boots. The staff is experienced on hiking terrains.
Sloppy burger. Too sour for my taste. Wonder if that's how it shd taste. Nonetheless, its all good.
Try all of them. Its so fun. Will come again.
You MUST TRY the homemade mushroom soup. #mushroomsouploverswillunderstand Food are affordable with friendly services. Oh don't forget to order the molten cake. While waiting, look at this pic!
